snippet.title: Disc Dimension: SteamVR Disc Golf Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
"Immerse yourself in the Disc Dimension, a captivating VR disc golf adventure where realistic physics converge with enchanting realms!  Wishlist on Steam today! https://store.steampowered.com/app/2699190/Disc_Dimension/

Roam through mystical landscapes, collecting elemental discs and conquering supernatural challenges. Use and develop your natural disc golf throwing motion, as you master all your favorite disc golf shots.  Join us in this mesmerizing virtual reality disc golf video game, where the fusion of real-world physics and mystical elements redefine disc golf!

Early Access Coming Soon to Steam VR!

Wishlist on Steam! https://store.steampowered.com/app/2699190/Disc_Dimension/
Join us on Discord! https://discord.gg/dT9BFuMQ
Discover more on the Disc Dimension Website! https://www.alchemygamestudio.com/disc-dimension

Developer Website: https://www.alchemygamestudio.com

Trailer Credits
-------------
Directed, Edited, Cinematography, and Sound by: Steve Hollinger
Assistant Directed by: Katie Hollinger
Music Composed by: Henrik Lindström
Voiceover by: Andrew Whelbig
Produced by: Alchemist Brew Game Studios

Disclaimer: All discs in Disc Dimension are fictional, and do not represent real discs, disc brands, or any disc manufacturing company or retailer.  The discs in this game are made solely for the purposes of playing this game, and any similar names or other likeness are purely accidental.
